o-chinas-navy-corruption/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="The Invisible Threat to China&rsquo;s Navy: Corruption" title="The Invisible Threat to China&rsquo;s Navy: Corruption" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat-2020-05-19-5.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat-2020-05-19-5.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat-2020-05-19-5.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Security</h5><h4>The Invisible Threat to China’s Navy: Corruption</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2020/05/chinas-growing-political-clout-in-nepal/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="China&rsquo;s Growing Political Clout in Nepal" title="China&rsquo;s Growing Political Clout in Nepal" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat-ap-19286484182110.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat-ap-19286484182110.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat-ap-19286484182110.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Diplomacy</h5><h4>China’s Growing Political Clout in Nepal</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2020/05/covid-19-a-reckoning-for-russias-asian-energy-aims/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="COVID-19: A Reckoning for Russia&rsquo;s Asian Energy Aims" title="COVID-19: A Reckoning for Russia&rsquo;s Asian Energy Aims" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat-2020-05-21.jpg 58